text: Muhammad Riaz Shaheen Bangash is a Pakistani politician who is member-elect of the Provincial Assembly of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa. ==Political career== Shaheen contested 2019 Khyber Pakhtunkhwa provincial election on 20 July 2019 from constituency PK-108 (Kurram-I) on the ticket of Jamiat Ulema-e-Islam (F). He won the election by the majority of 602 votes over the independent runner up Malik Jameel Khan. He garnered 12,240 votes while Khan received 11,638 votes. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Jamiat Ulema-e-Islam (F) politicians Category:Politicians from Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
